            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-6-1679409882323-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with your<strong> chipotle paste</strong> (cant handle the heat? Go easy!) in a bowl and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-6-1679409886354-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-6-1679409886354-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-6-1679409886354-x700.jpg",
