          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-6-1679409886354-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p><p>Remove 1 <strong>outer lettuce leaf</strong> per person and set aside for serving</p><p>Tear the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> torn lettuce leaves</strong> to a bowl and mix with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season lightly with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>crisp lettuce salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-6-1679409907646-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-6-1679409907646-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-6-1679409907646-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-6-1679409907646-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-6-1679409907646-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> beef burger patty[ies]</strong>, press them down firmly with a spatula and cook for 5 min</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-high, flip each patty and cook for a further 5 min or until charred and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Keep pressing the patty[ies] down with a spatula to keep them flat</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-6-1679409913232-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
